OL,4,CFacebook adds 'expert' feature to
OL,5,Cgroups
OL,6, Facebook is rolling out a way to
OL,7, designate topic "experts" inside
OL,8, user-run Facebook groups.
OL,10,FThe social network says the new feature
OL,11,Fis designed to help real experts "stand
OL,12,Fout" in discussions about their field
OL,13,Fof expertise.
OL,15,FGroup admins will have the power to
OL,16,Fgive the title to nearly any member
OL,17,Fthey want.
OL,19,FThat means groups promoting conspiracy
OL,20,Ftheories or fringe views will also be
OL,21,Fable to designate "experts".
